  {
    "id": "faq_content_code",
    "name": "code",
    "parent": "faq_content_container",
    "children": [],
    "settings": {
      "code": "<!-- FAQ CONTENT SECTION -->\n<section class=\"faq-content-section\">\n  <div class=\"faq-content-wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"faq-list\">\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>How much does it cost?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>Prices range from 69,900 CZK (Economic Package) to 89,200 CZK (Premium Care Package). Everything is included in the price - flight tickets, 5-star hotel accommodation, VIP transport, surgery, PRP therapy. No hidden fees.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>What is included in the price?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>Everything! Round-trip flight, 3 nights in a 5-star hotel, VIP transport, pre-operative examination, transplant (unlimited grafts within safe limits), PRP therapy, cosmetic package, post-operative care, Czech support from Michaela 24/7, travel insurance, and certificate.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Is it painful?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>The procedure is performed under local anesthesia, so you don't feel pain. Some clients may feel slight pressure, but nothing painful. After the procedure, you may experience mild discomfort, which can be relieved with common medications.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Are the results permanent?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>Yes! Transplanted hair is resistant to hair loss and will stay with you permanently. They are your own hair from the donor area, which is genetically programmed to grow permanently.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Why is your price lower than competitors?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>We are a direct clinic without intermediaries. Most Czech companies just mediate - they add a 30-50% markup. You communicate directly with us and pay directly to us. No markup = up to 30% lower price.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>How long does the procedure take?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>The procedure usually takes 6-8 hours depending on the number of grafts. The entire stay in Istanbul is 3 nights - the day before surgery, the day of surgery, and the day after surgery.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>When will I see results?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>New hair begins to grow after 3-4 months. Full results are visible after 12-18 months. During this time, we provide follow-up care and consultations.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Do I need to shave my head?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>With the DHI method, head shaving is not necessary! Your hair can be preserved, which is a great advantage. With the Sapphire FUE method, the donor area is usually shaved, but you can keep your hair longer to cover the donor area.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>What is the success rate of the transplant?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>The transplant success rate is 85-95%. Most clients are very satisfied with the results. It is important to follow post-operative instructions and care.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Can I get a transplant even with advanced baldness?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>Yes, transplantation is possible even with advanced hair loss. During the consultation, we will determine whether you have a sufficient donor area for the desired result. If not, we will suggest a realistic plan.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>What is the difference between the DHI and Sapphire FUE methods?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>The DHI method uses a special pen (implanter) for direct graft implantation without prior channel creation. Sapphire FUE uses sapphire blades to create channels and then grafts are implanted. Both methods are gentle and effective.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>How many grafts can be transplanted?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>The number of grafts depends on your donor area and desired result. Typically, 2,000-5,000 grafts are transplanted. Our packages include an unlimited number of grafts within safe medical limits.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>How long does healing take?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>The first week is the most important. Scabs fall off after 7-14 days. After 2-3 weeks, you can resume normal activities. Transplanted hair may shed after 2-4 weeks (this is normal), new hair begins to grow after 3-4 months.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Can I exercise after the transplant?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>It is important to avoid physical activity during the first week. After 2-3 weeks, you can start with light exercise. We recommend intense and contact sports only after one month.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Can I drink alcohol after the transplant?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>Alcohol is not recommended during the first week after the procedure, as it can slow down healing. After a week, you can drink in moderation, but we recommend waiting until complete healing.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Will I need a second procedure?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>It depends on your situation. If you have advanced baldness or want a denser result, a second procedure may be necessary. During the consultation, we will suggest a realistic plan.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>How does the consultation work?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>The consultation is free and without obligations. You can have it online or in person. We will discuss your situation, show you your options, and suggest a plan. Michaela will respond to you.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>How do you arrange flights and hotel?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>We arrange everything for you! After confirming the procedure, we will arrange your round-trip flight to Istanbul, a reservation at a 5-star hotel, and VIP transport from the airport to the hotel and clinic. You don't have to worry about anything.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Is it safe to travel to Turkey?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>Yes, Istanbul is a safe city and a popular destination for medical tourism. We have experience with thousands of clients from all over Europe. Everything is organized and safe.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>What is PRP Therapy?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>PRP (Platelet-Rich Plasma) is a therapy that accelerates healing and hair growth. Your blood is drawn, centrifuged, and applied to the scalp. It is included in the price of all packages.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Can I transplant a beard or eyebrows?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>Yes! We offer beard and eyebrow transplantation. The process is similar to hair transplantation. Grafts are extracted from the head and implanted into the beard or eyebrow area.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>How long before the procedure should I stop taking medications?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>It depends on the type of medication. Some blood-thinning medications (aspirin, warfarin) need to be discontinued 1-2 weeks before the procedure. We will provide you with detailed instructions during the consultation.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Can I get a transplant if I have a skin condition?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>It depends on the type of condition. Some skin conditions (e.g., psoriasis, eczema) may be contraindications. We will discuss this during the consultation and determine whether transplantation is suitable for you.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>What is the minimum age requirement?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>We recommend transplantation for individuals over 25 years old, as hair loss may continue until that age. For younger individuals, it is important to carefully evaluate the situation.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Can I get a transplant if I am a woman?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>Yes! Hair transplantation is also suitable for women. We have experience with transplants for women and use a more gentle approach. The DHI method allows transplantation without head shaving, which is an advantage for women.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>How long do I have to wait for an appointment?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>Appointments are usually available within 2-4 weeks. During the season (summer), the waiting time may be longer. We recommend booking an appointment in advance.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Can I cancel or change my appointment?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>Yes, you can change or cancel your appointment. Details about cancellation conditions can be found in our terms and conditions. Usually, the appointment can be changed without a fee with sufficient advance notice.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>How does post-operative care work?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>We provide detailed instructions for post-operative care. Michaela is available 24/7 for any questions. Long-term care and follow-up consultations are included in the Standard Plus and Premium Care packages.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Can I dye my hair after the transplant?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>After complete healing (approximately 1 month), you can dye your hair. We recommend using gentle dyes and consulting with us before the first dyeing.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>What guarantee is there on results?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>We provide a certificate of the procedure. If there are any problems with healing or hair growth, we provide follow-up care. The success rate is 85-95%, but individual results may vary.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\">\n          <span>Can I pay in installments?</span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <p>We will discuss payment options during the consultation. Usually, it is possible to pay a deposit and the remaining balance before the procedure or upon arrival in Istanbul.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');\n\n  :root {\n    --primary-gold: #E5C158;\n    --secondary-gold: #D4AF37;\n    --dark-gray: #1A1A1A;\n    --black: #000000;\n    --white: #FFFFFF;\n    --light-gray: #F5F5F5;\n    --medium-gray: #333333;\n  }\n\n  .faq-content-section {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    background: var(--white);\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    padding: clamp(50px, 8vw, 100px) clamp(20px, 4vw, 60px);\n  }\n\n  .faq-content-wrapper {\n    max-width: 900px;\n    width: 100%;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .faq-content-section .faq-list {\n    margin-top: clamp(30px, 4vw, 40px);\n  }\n\n  .faq-content-section .faq-item {\n    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--light-gray);\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .faq-content-section .faq-item:last-child {\n    border-bottom: none;\n  }\n\n  .faq-content-section .faq-question {\n    width: 100%;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    padding: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px) 0;\n    background: transparent;\n    border: none;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    text-align: left;\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 18px);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .faq-content-section .faq-question:hover {\n    color: var(--primary-gold);\n  }\n\n  .faq-content-section .faq-icon {\n    width: clamp(28px, 3vw, 32px);\n    height: clamp(28px, 3vw, 32px);\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 28px);\n    color: var(--primary-gold);\n    transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    font-weight: 300;\n  }\n\n  .faq-item.active .faq-content-section .faq-icon {\n    transform: rotate(45deg);\n  }\n\n  .faq-content-section .faq-answer {\n    max-height: 0;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    transition: max-height 0.4s ease;\n  }\n\n  .faq-item.active .faq-content-section .faq-answer {\n    max-height: 500px;\n  }\n\n  .faq-content-section .faq-answer p {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(14px, 1.8vw, 16px);\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin: 0 0 24px 0;\n    padding-right: 40px;\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .faq-content-section {\n      padding: clamp(40px, 6vw, 60px) clamp(20px, 4vw, 24px);\n    }\n\n    .faq-content-section .faq-question {\n      font-size: clamp(15px, 1.8vw, 17px);\n      padding: clamp(14px, 1.8vw, 18px) 0;\n    }\n\n    .faq-content-section .faq-answer p {\n      padding-right: 0;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<script>\n  // FAQ Accordion - All Sections\n  (function() {\n    function initAllFAQ() {\n      var containers = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-list, .faq-items, .faq-grid');\n      for (var c = 0; c < containers.length; c++) {\n        var faqContainer = containers[c];\n        if (faqContainer.dataset.faqInit) continue;\n        faqContainer.dataset.faqInit = 'true';\n        (function(container) {\n          container.addEventListener('click', function(e) {\n            var question = e.target.closest('.faq-question');\n            if (!question) return;\n            var item = question.closest('.faq-item');\n            if (!item) return;\n            var isActive = item.classList.contains('active');\n            var allItems = container.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');\n            for (var i = 0; i < allItems.length; i++) {\n              allItems[i].classList.remove('active');\n            }\n            if (!isActive) {\n              item.classList.add('active');\n            }\n          });\n        })(faqContainer);\n      }\n    }\n    if (document.readyState === 'loading') {\n      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initAllFAQ);\n    } else {\n      initAllFAQ();\n    }\n    setTimeout(initAllFAQ, 100);\n    setTimeout(initAllFAQ, 500);\n  })();\n</script>",
